    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single gap (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted because the tested condition represents the governing worst-case loading per ASTM F1717. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-established acceptance bounds. The validation result generated under ModelConfiguration ansys-mechanical-2026-q1-build-7-rc2 is considered applicable to the released build ansys-mechanical-2026-q1-build-7 on the basis of the vendor change log confirming no solver-kernel modifications between the release candidate and the production release. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level for this Class II device COU.",
